data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Port Orange's coveted Foxboro subdivision! This stunning single-family residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2-car garage. As you step inside, the gleaming new roof and recently upgraded AC promise worry-free living.The kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring modern cabinets and exquisite granite countertops - perfect for both everyday meals and entertaining guests. Picture yourself enjoying morning coffee in the cozy breakfast nook, basking in the abundant natural light that fills the space.But the real showstopper? Your own private oasis awaits in the backyard - a sparkling pool invites you to unwind after a long day or host lively gatherings with friends and family. Imagine summer BBQs and refreshing swims in this ... idyllic setting! And for those cozy evenings, a wood-burning fireplace sets the perfect ambiance in the living room.

Beyond the beauty within, this home's location is truly unbeatable. Nestled in Foxboro, you'll find yourself in a community that exudes charm and tranquility. Convenience is at your fingertips with shopping, schools, and restaurants just a stone's throw away. Need to grab groceries or enjoy a night out? You're minutes from it all!

Explore the nearby schools that promise top-notch education for your family. Take a leisurely stroll to discover the vibrant local dining scene or head to the nearby shopping centers for a retail therapy session. The array of attractions ensures that you'll never run out of things to do!

Seize the opportunity to make this house your home - an oasis of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss out on the chance to experience the best of Port Orange living in the charming Foxboro community. Schedule your showing today and step into a future filled with endless possibilities!
